1
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:04,600
Your Majesty,

2
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:06,440
you've been coughing lately,

3
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,880
and sleeping poorly at night.

4
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:09,880
Why not summon another physician?

5
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:10,960
No need.

6
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:14,520
I know my own body well.

7
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:17,040
Do not let A Ling know about this.

8
00:02:22,079 --> 00:02:22,880
Your Majesty.

9
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:25,460
Why have you been avoiding me lately?

10
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,460
Your Majesty, Your Highness.

11
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:31,680
I shall take my leave.

12
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,720
It smells like medicine.

13
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:39,250
Has your old illness returned?

14
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:41,280
No, it hasn't.

15
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,360
I am fine.

16
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:46,079
But there is clearly

17
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,090
a smell of medicine in here.

18
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:54,160
You wouldn't happen to be preparing...

19
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,440
What?

20
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:07,560
Nothing.

21
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:10,640
I came to tell you

22
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:12,680
that you don't have to avoid me.

23
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,880
I won't force you.

24
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:17,240
Keep preparing.

25
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:18,450
I'm leaving.

26
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,800
Your Highness, you've been sighing since you returned from Changan Palace.

27
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,600
What's wrong?

28
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:50,010
What exactly is the matter?

29
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:52,120
Li Yunxi refuses to consummate the marriage

30
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:54,050
because he has a physical problem.

31
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,600
Then these clothes for the little prince,

32
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:59,000
should I still make them?

33
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,040
We haven't even consummated the marriage yet.

34
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:03,040
Why are you in such a rush to prepare?

35
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,840
Consort Xue has been banished to the Cold Palace,

36
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,800
and you and His Majesty are very close.

37
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,320
I thought they would be needed sooner or later,

38
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,980
so I prepared them in advance.

39
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,840
For the little prince.

40
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:21,760
Hanxing.

41
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:25,420
You are very skilled at making baby clothes.

42
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,320
Do you like children?

43
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:32,000
I heard

44
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:35,010
that you entered the palace two years ago.

45
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:37,480
Where were you before entering the palace?

46
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,360
You jinx!

47
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:53,120
You made me lose all my money!

48
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:55,170
Don't hit me!

49
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,760
Don't hit me!

50
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,720
Please!

51
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:09,960
Save my child!

52
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:16,080
That the lady survived,

53
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:17,480
is already a miracle.

54
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:18,560
However,

55
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:21,320
I'm afraid she can no longer bear children.

56
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:26,760
It's okay.

57
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:29,410
It's all in the past.

58
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:35,040
Later, my benefactor saved me.

59
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:38,480
He avenged me,

60
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:40,600
and gave me a new name.

61
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:42,600
I have nowhere to go.

62
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:44,920
Please take me in.

63
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,360
The night is cold,

64
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,260
but the stars are shining.

65
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,720
From now on,

66
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:51,240
your name shall be

67
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:53,040
Hanxing.

68
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,330
Your benefactor

69
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:58,800
must be a very gentle person.

70
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,440
Very gentle.

71
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:05,800
I will watch over him for the rest of my life.

72
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:07,520
Hanxing,

73
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,580
when you mention Li Yunmo,

74
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,400
your eyes are full of love.

75
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,320
Abdicate the throne.

76
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,080
I believe

77
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,770
Li Yunmo will be a good emperor.

78
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,159
Your Majesty, you...

79
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:34,200
You...

80
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,040
What I mean is,

81
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,440
fate is unpredictable.

82
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,600
What if I were to succumb to illness?

83
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:46,640
Your Majesty,

84
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:49,200
although you were frail in your youth...

85
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:50,659
But you are still so young.

86
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:52,960
Why say such depressing things?

87
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,740
Why are you crying?

88
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,400
It won't be that soon.

89
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:08,080
Your Majesty.

90
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:10,930
If something unfortunate really happens to you,

91
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:13,360
and you leave the State of Li to Prince Qi,

92
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:15,160
what will happen to the Empress?

93
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:19,200
Prince Qi has long coveted the Empress.

94
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,320
Do you really intend

95
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,960
to simply hand her over?

96
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,720
Put it away.

97
00:07:47,159 --> 00:07:49,420
It looks like it's gotten shorter again.

98
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:52,520
Where exactly did this incense come from?

99
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:54,680
Why have I searched through every book,

100
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:56,210
yet cannot find its origin?

101
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,780
Your Highness, Prince Qi is here.

102
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,010
Let's go.

103
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:17,440
Why did you summon me here all of a sudden?

104
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:19,440
To invite you for a drink, of course.

105
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,200
You are being attentive for no reason.

106
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:22,530
You must be up to no good.

107
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:24,160
What?

108
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:27,320
Don't you dare drink the wine I gave you?

109
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:30,720
You...

110
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,760
look happier these past two days

111
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:34,690
than you have in the last two years.

112
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:37,480
Being in sync with the one I love

113
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,539
naturally makes me happy.

114
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,200
If one day

115
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,900
I could be like you,

116
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,450
that would be great.

117
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,080
I'm afraid that will be hard.

118
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:57,280
Prince Qi,

119
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:00,640
you love yourself more.

120
00:09:04,680 --> 00:09:05,610
What do you mean?

121
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:12,460
What are you doing?

122
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:13,680
Nothing.

123
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:16,480
I just asked Prince Qi over for a drink.

124
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:18,250
We used to do this often.

125
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,800
That was before.

126
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,120
Not anymore.

127
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:24,880
You are my woman.

128
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,920
I won't allow it.

129
00:09:35,280 --> 00:09:36,540
What is Xiao Ling up to?

130
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:40,000
Her Highness says His Majesty has been avoiding her.

131
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,600
She wants to make him jealous

132
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:44,160
to bring them closer.

133
00:09:58,640 --> 00:09:59,880
Why are you and Li Yunmo

134
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:01,340
drinking together again?

135
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:03,840
Your Majesty,

136
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,500
you are so jealous.

137
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:14,560
So,

138
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:18,440
you're provoking me on purpose?

139
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,120
I was thinking,

140
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:23,160
instead of letting you take your time,

141
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:24,840
I should just

142
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,600
give you a strong dose.

143
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:37,640
Who... Who said I...

144
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:39,680
I drink medicine to...

145
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:41,770
Okay.

146
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:43,100
Then what is it for?

147
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:50,240
You...

148
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:55,400
What strong dose do you plan to give me?

149
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,280
For Your Majesty,

150
00:10:59,080 --> 00:10:59,760
am I not

151
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,240
the best strong dose?

152
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:10,880
Now that Your Majesty is so jealous,

153
00:11:11,520 --> 00:11:13,980
it's the perfect time for our wedding night.

154
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,000
A-Ling,

155
00:12:04,920 --> 00:12:05,800
if I die,

156
00:12:06,640 --> 00:12:07,570
what will you do?

157
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,880
Why do you keep staring at me?

158
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:18,960
It feels like a dream.

159
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:23,860
This isn't a dream.

160
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:27,120
We'll be together forever.

161
00:12:27,760 --> 00:12:30,240
Always by each other's side.

162
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:38,360
By the way,

163
00:12:40,040 --> 00:12:41,680
you seem healthy.

164
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:43,850
What medicine were you taking?

165
00:12:48,520 --> 00:12:50,160
You know Su Kuang.

166
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,080
He nags a lot.

167
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:54,580
He always wants me to take tonics.

168
00:12:55,560 --> 00:12:56,600
He is loyal.

169
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,100
It's for your own good.

170
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:00,560
I know.

171
00:13:03,400 --> 00:13:04,160
A-Ling, I...

172
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:07,610
You go first.

173
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:13,000
I...

174
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:17,380
am tired of life in the palace.

175
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:20,500
I want to pass the throne to Yun Mo.

176
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:24,240
Let's go out for a walk and take a look.

177
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:28,940
I was thinking the same thing.

178
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:30,720
You've stayed in the Capital since childhood

179
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:32,720
and never seen the scenery outside.

180
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:35,800
I'll take you to the frontier to see the desert sunset,

181
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:38,880
take you beyond the Great Wall to ride horses freely,

182
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:39,880
and take you to see the southern mountains.

183
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:41,340
We'll go down to Jiangnan.

184
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:43,500
Let's go visit my father-in-law.

185
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:44,640
Okay.

186
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:47,360
Then we'll travel all the way to Jiangnan.

187
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,490
If you like it there,

188
00:13:48,680 --> 00:13:50,080
we can settle down there.

189
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,220
We set off soon,

190
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:53,650
arrive in March,

191
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:56,920
just in time for the beautiful scenery of Jiangnan.

192
00:13:56,920 --> 00:13:58,320
After we visit Jiangnan,

193
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:02,680
we'll go to other places.

194
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:04,570
How does that sound?

195
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:05,760
Good.

196
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,200
Whatever you say.

197
00:14:12,880 --> 00:14:13,400
Ling.

198
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,610
I don't have much time left.

199
00:14:16,160 --> 00:14:17,680
I can only rest assured

200
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,160
after I send you to the General's side.
